{
  "apigatewayv2.apimapping.CfnAbout": "The `AWS::ApiGatewayV2::ApiMapping` resource contains an API mapping. An API mapping relates a path of your custom domain name to a stage of your API. A custom domain name can have multiple API mappings, but the paths can't overlap. A custom domain can map only to APIs of the same protocol type. For more information, see [CreateApiMapping](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigatewayv2/latest/api-reference/domainnames-domainname-apimappings.html",
